    <title>远程SSH到多台主机执行命令</title>
    <link href="http://yoursite.com/2017/12/01/ssh_automation/"/>
    <id>http://yoursite.com/2017/12/01/ssh_automation/</id>
    <published>2017-12-01T07:55:23.000Z</published>
    <updated>2017-12-01T08:14:32.132Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<ol><li>直接命令行执行使用ssh操作，顺序执行效率低，且如果没有设置免密，需要重复执行密码<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">for i in `cat host.txt`;do ssh -t cisco@$i &quot;sudo uptime&quot;; done          </div><div class="line">#-t参数表示可以输入sudo（允许建立tty用于sudo）</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ol><p>或者</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">for i in 192.168.1.&#123;1..5&#125;;do ssh -t cisco@$i &quot;sudo uptime&quot;; done</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ol><li><p>Shell的另一种实现：</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div><div class="line">5</div><div class="line">6</div><div class="line">7</div><div class="line">8</div><div class="line">9</div><div class="line">10</div><div class="line">11</div><div class="line">12</div><div class="line">13</div><div class="line">14</div><div class="line">15</div><div class="line">16</div><div class="line">17</div><div class="line">18</div><div class="line">19</div><div class="line">20</div><div class="line">21</div><div class="line">22</div><div class="line">23</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">#!/bin/bash</div><div class="line">start_time=`date +%s`</div><div class="line">[ -e /tmp/fd1 ] || mkfifo /tmp/fd1</div><div class="line">exec 3&lt;&gt;/tmp/fd1</div><div class="line">rm -rf /tmp/fd1</div><div class="line">for ((i=1;i&lt;=5;i++))</div><div class="line">do</div><div class="line">    echo &gt;&amp;3</div><div class="line">done</div><div class="line">while read line</div><div class="line">do</div><div class="line">    read -u3</div><div class="line">    &#123;</div><div class="line">    host=`echo $line| awk &apos;&#123;print $1&#125;&apos;`</div><div class="line">    ssh  root@$host &apos;echo “123”&apos;</div><div class="line">    echo &apos;success,&apos;$host</div><div class="line">    echo &gt;&amp;3</div><div class="line">    &#125;&amp;</div><div class="line">done &lt; host.txt</div><div class="line">stop_time=`date +%s`</div><div class="line">echo &quot;time: `expr $stop_time - $start_time`&quot;</div><div class="line">exec 3&lt;&amp;-</div><div class="line">exec 3&gt;&amp;-</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>pssh方法，可以实现并发执行多台主机，但是没法用普通用户执行sudo<br>需要提前pip install pssh安装</p></li></ol><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">pssh -i -H 192.168.18.129 -A &quot;uptime&quot;    #指定单台主机</div><div class="line">pssh -i -h host.txt -A &quot;uptime&quot;          #指定主机列表文件</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><img src="/images/1.png" alt="1"></p>]]></content>
    
